            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Imperator Caesar, son of the divine Antoninus, grandson of the divine Hadrian, great-grandson of the divine Trajan (conqueror of) Parthia, great-great grandson of the divine Nerva, Lucius Aurelius Verus Augustus, holder of tribunician power for the 2nd time, consul twice. The 7th cohort of vigiles (dedicated this).</p>
